New England Investment and Retirement Group, Inc. | Wealth Management North Andover, MA



































New England Investment and Retirement Group, Inc.

Search







Search for:



 








Founded in 1995, New England Investment and Retirement Group, Inc. operates out of North Andover, Massachusetts under the leadership of founder Nicholas Giacoumakis.
New England Investment and Retirement Group, Inc. provides the following wealth management services for clients: investment management; retirement and sufficiency planning; estate and charitable planning; risk management and asset protection. Each client is able to turn to New England Investment and Retirement Group, Inc. for education, communication, and quality service while the Firm attempts to help them make better informed financial decisions as they become financially independent.
New England Investment and Retirement Group, Inc. is focused on providing unbiased advice for each client. This advice is developed by a staff averaging nearly 17 years of experience in the wealth management industry, who communicate with a network of business alliances that includes attorneys, accountants, estate planning specialists, and several other third-party financial consultants. Today the Firm hopes that its level of expertise will allow clients to obtain financial independence. This is possible in part because the Firm is committed to the same vision that it had in 1995:

Offer a wide array of planning services.
Make a commitment to safeguarding the interests of each client.
Deliver an unparalleled level of personalized service.
Use time-honored investment traditions to help clients achieve their lifestyle and legacy goals.

New England Investment and Retirement Group, Inc. uses a model-based approach that allows it to avoid the pitfalls that affect many other financial advisory firms. When other firms grow, many have trouble tracking, analyzing, and managing each individual client’s account while continuing to grow and build their businesses. New England Investment and Retirement Group, Inc. designed a truly scalable investment management process that allows the Firm to consistently deliver high quality customer service even as the Firm grows.





